com.github.davidmoten.rx2.flowable

Class Serialized

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.davidmoten.rx2.flowable.Serialized

  • public final class Serialized
extends Object
    Utility class for writing Flowable streams to ObjectOutputStreams and reading Flowable streams of indeterminate size from ObjectInputStreams.
